Final Answer:

Here are three apartment buildings that meet your criteria:

1. Wilson Place
   - Address: 15 E Lane Ave, Columbus, OH 43201
   - Phone: (380) 888-2655
   - Website: https://www.wilsonplaceapartments.com

2. The Aubrey
   - Address: 114 East Fifth Avenue, Columbus, Ohio 43201
   - Phone: (614) 796-0164
   - Website: https://www.livetheaubrey.com

3. University Village
   - Address: 2981 Olentangy River Road, Columbus, OH 43202
   - Phone: (614) 261-1211
   - Website: https://www.universityvillage.com

All three apartments offer one-bedroom units under $1300 per month, are within a 20-minute drive from Ohio State University, and have parking and elevator access.

